[Elderly people, dependency and vulnerability in the coronavirus pandemic: an 
emergency for a social and health integration].

[Article in Spanish]

Porcel-Gálvez AM(1), Badanta B(2), Barrientos-Trigo S(1), Lima-Serrano M(3).

Author information:
(1)Equipo de coordinación TEC-MED (ENI CBC MED - Europe). Desarrollo de un 
